ival.nl/prijs-van-de-nederlandse-filmkritiek/ |website=Nederlands Film Festival |accessdate=12 April 2020 |language=nl-NL |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217110827/https://www.filmfestival.nl/prijs-van-de-nederlandse-filmkritiek/ |archive-date=17 December 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|- \n| 1989\n| ''[[Squatter's Delight|In krakende welstand]]'' \n| Director & Screenwriter\n| De Prijs van de stad Utrecht at the [[Netherlands Film Festival]].<ref name=\"Scherp\" />\n|}\n\n== Awards ==\n* 2007: [[Golden Calf for Best Director]] and Prize of the Dutch Film Critics (Prijs van de Nederlandse Filmkritiek) for ''Tussenstand''<ref name=\"BR\">{{cite web |title=Beste Regie \u22c6 Nederlands Film Festival |url=https://www.filmfestival.nl/gouden-kalveren/beste-regie/ |website=Nederlands Film Festival |accessdate=12 April 2020 |language=nl-NL |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601013716/https://www.filmfestival.nl/gouden-kalveren/beste-regie/ |archive-date=1 June 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\"FK\">{{cite web |title=Prijs van de Nederlandse Filmkritiek \u22c6 Nederlands Film Festival |url=https://www.filmfestival.nl/prijs-van-de-nederlandse-filmkritiek/ |website=Nederlands Film Festival |accessdate=12 April 2020 |language=nl-NL |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217110827/https://www.filmfestival.nl/prijs-van-de-nederlandse-filmkritiek/ |archive-date=17 December 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n* 2005: Crystal Bear award at the [[Berlin International Film Festival]] for ''BlueBird''.<ref name=\"WAC\">{{cite web |title=Katia's Sister (Het Zusje Van Katia) |url=https://walkerart.org/calendar/2009/katias-sister-het-zusje-van-katia |website=Walker Art Center |accessdate=12 April 2020}}</ref>  \n* 1993: Prize of the Dutch Film Critics (Prijs van de Nederlandse Filmkritiek) for ''Love Hurts'' (''Hartverscheurend)''.<ref name=\"FK\" />   \n* 1993: Swissair/Crossair Special Prize at the [[Locarno Festival]] for ''Love Hurts''.<ref name=\