{"title_page": "Sandata", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Sandata\n| cover      =Sandatasarahgeronimo.jpg\n| alt        =\n| border     = yes\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Sarah Geronimo]]\n| album      = [[This 15 Me]]\n| released   = {{start date|2018|01|12}}\n| format     = [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| recorded   = 2018\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = {{Flat list|\n*[[Pop music|Pop]]\n*[[Electronic dance music|EDM]]\n}}\n| length     = 3:37\n| label      = [[Viva Records (Philippines)|Viva Records]]\n| writer     = {{Flat list|\n*Nica del Rosario\n*Julius de Belen\n}}\n| producer   =\n| prev_title = [[I Just Fall in Love Again|Just Fall In Love Again]]\n| prev_year  =\n| next_title = [[Ganito]]\n| next_year  =\n}}'''Sandata''' ({{translation|Weapon}}) is the lead single from Sarah Geronimo's album ''[[This 15 Me]]'' released on January 12, 2018. The song was written by Nica del Rosario who also wrote her previous hits [[Tala (song)|''Tala'']] and ''Minamahal''. During her set at the 2018 International Balloon and Music Festival in [[Lubao, Pampanga|Pampanga]] on March 24, she performed the song for the very first time. [[CNN Philippines]] named the song as the \"Best Filipino Song of 2018.\"\n\n== Release history ==\nThe song became available for pre-order on [[iTunes]] on January 10 and became the second most pre-ordered song during that time. On January 12, the day of its release, it went straight to number one on iTunes Philippines Songs Chart and stayed on top for four consecutive days. It also landed on [[Spotify]] Philippines Viral 50 at number 23. As of April 2018, the song has been played 800,000 times on Spotify, despite not having radio airplay and promotions.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://twitter.com/iSGFanboy/status/982041062469349376|title=Fanboying SG on Twitter|work=Twitter|access-date=2018-04-06|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.lionheartv.net/2018/01/sarah-geronimos-latest-single-sandata-debuts-1-itunes-ph/|title=Sarah Geronimo's latest single \"Sandata\" debuts at #1 in iTunes PH - LionhearTV|website=www.lionheartv.net|access-date=2018-04-06}}</ref>\n\n== Music video ==\nThe official lyric video of the song was published on [[Viva Records (Philippines)|Viva Records]]' official [[YouTube]] channel on January 20, 2018. Its music video is yet to be released.<ref>{{Citation|last=Viva Records|title=Sarah Geronimo \u2014 Sandata [Official Lyric Video]|date=2018-01-20|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mG1b6b3nDb4|accessdate=2018-04-06}}</ref>. On June 27, 2018 Viva Records confirms on their Facebook page release the teaser of Music Video and release on July 1, 2018. The music video is Directed by Paul Basinilio and it premieres on [[myx|MYX]].\n\n== Live performances ==\nSarah Geronimo performed the song on International Balloon and Music Festival 2018, held in [[Lubao, Pampanga]] on March 24, 2018. She also performed the song on her 15th anniversary concert ''[[This 15 Me]]'' on April 14, 2018. On [[ASAP (variety show)|ASAP]] stage, she performed the song on May 27, 2018.<ref>{{Citation|last=JMYoutubeChannel|title=Sarah Geronimo \"SANDATA\" at Lubao International Balloon and Music Festival 2018|date=2018-03-25|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T5Xe60u93LI|accessdate=2018-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=ABS-CBN Entertainment|title=ASAP: Sarah G performs latest single \"Sandata\" on #ASAPSummerPlay|date=2018-05-27|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jlxcAqDqBNE|accessdate=2018-05-30}}</ref>\n\n== Reception ==\nSandata made it to the list \"7 new local music releases to listen to\" made by [[CNN Philippines]], according to the article, \"the song continues Sarah Geronimo's streak of Filipino dance pop anthems that began with [[Ikot-Ikot|''Ikot-ikot'']]'' then led us to [[Kilometro (song)|Kilometro]] and [[Tala (song)|Tala]]''. While its production feels more low-key, less anthemic than past turns, ''Sandata'' makes up for it by finding Geronimo at her most polished and nuanced. This one's a grower, and as far as Filipino pop goes, it's a risk well-taken.\"<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://cnnphilippines.com/life/entertainment/music/2018/03/08/new-local-music-releases.html|title=7 new local music releases to listen to|work=cnn|access-date=2018-04-06|language=en}}</ref>\n\n''<nowiki/>''\n\n<nowiki/>''<nowiki/>''<nowiki/>''<nowiki/>''\n== iTunes Charts ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n! scope=\"col\" |Chart (2018)\n! scope=\"col\" |Position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |Philippines\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |1<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.abs-cbn.com/entertainment/01/13/18/sarah-g-strikes-with-sandata-instantly-tops-chart|title=Sarah G strikes with 'Sandata', instantly tops chart|last=News|first=ABS-CBN|work=ABS-CBN News|access-date=2018-04-06|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |Singapore\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |86<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://twitter.com/sarahgpopster/status/952364154093944832|title=Popster Nica \ud83d\udc93 on Twitter|work=Twitter|access-date=2018-04-06|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |Papua New Guinea\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |72<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://twitter.com/DarkEgo1/status/951652606840983552|title=\u2605DarkEgo\u2605 on Twitter|work=Twitter|access-date=2018-04-06|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n[[Category:2018 songs]]\n[[Category:Sarah Geronimo songs]]\n[[Category:2018 singles]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Sandata\n| cover      =Sandatasarahgeronimo.jpg\n| alt        =\n| border     = yes\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Sarah Geronimo]]\n| album      = [[This 15 Me]]\n| released   = {{start date|2018|01|12}}\n| format     = [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| recorded   = 2018\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = {{Flat list|\n*[[Pop music|Pop]]\n*[[Electronic dance music|EDM]]\n}}\n| length     = 3:37\n| label      = [[Viva Records (Philippines)|Viva Reco